ActCanada National Parks Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the NATIONAL PARKS WILDERNESS AREA DECLARATION REGULATIONS which would establish four new wilderness areas in the national parks (Waterton Lakes-Alberta, Fundy-New Brunswick, Vuntut -Yukon Territory), a national park reserve (Nahanni-Northwest Territories), as well as new wilderness map numbers describing the limits of the new declared wilderness areas.
